---

## ğŸ¯ **Configuration**
You can modify **file paths** in `config.json`:
```json
{
  "input_paths": {
    "ec3epd": "input/ec3epd.csv",
    "tru": "input/tru.csv",
    "mcp": "input/mcp.csv"
  },
  "output_paths": {
    "ec3epd": "output/ec3epd.ttl",
    "tru": "output/tru.ttl",
    "mcp": "output/mcp.ttl",
    "merged": "output/merged_ontology.ttl"
  }
}
```

